  "instructions": [
    "Wash all vegetables thoroughly and dry them.",
    "Separate the baby pak choi into bite‑size pieces and set aside.",
    "Dice the red bell pepper, cucumber, and carrot into thin matchsticks.",
    "Zest the lime and squeeze its juice into a small bowl.",
    "Add sesame oil, rice vinegar, low‑sodium soy sauce, grated ginger, and garlic‑infused oil to the lime juice and whisk until combined.",
    "Toss the vegetables with the dressing until evenly coated.",
    "Fold in the mint leaves and roasted peanuts, mixing gently.",
    "Refrigerate the salad for at least 10 minutes to chill and let flavors meld.",
    "Serve cold, optionally garnishing with extra mint or lime wedges."
